OL,3,CWalsall residents heartbroken after
OL,4,Csewage flooded their homes
OL,6,FResidents living in the town of
OL,7,FWillenhall near Walsall say they have
OL,8,Fbeen left heartbroken and devastated
OL,9,Fat the state of their homes after
OL,10,Fsewage flooded them 3 weeks ago.
OL,12,FYoung families and elderly people are
OL,13,Famong those living in the houses which
OL,14,Fhave been covered in thick sludge as a
OL,15,Fresult of the flood.
OL,17,FResidents on Farmbridge Way say they
OL,18,Foften wade through the sludge, that is
OL,19,Fsometimes hip height.
