OL,3,CWalsall residents heartbroken after
OL,4,Csewage flooded their homes
OL,6,FSharon Sleeth has lived there for more
OL,7,Fthan 30 years, during which time her
OL,8,Fhouse has been flooded with sewage
OL,9,Ffour times.
OL,11,F"We've had it six inches up the walls,
OL,12,F8 inches, to the point where had to
OL,13,Flose half the wall with plasterboard
OL,14,Fthroughout the house.
OL,16,F"Things have been destroyed, furniture
OL,17,Fhas been destroyed. It leaves a black
OL,18,Fscum, you could literally write your
OL,19,Fname in it, it's like black sand, the
OL,20,Fsmell is horrendous."
