OL,3,CWalsall residents heartbroken after
OL,4,Csewage flooded their homes
OL,6,FHeavy thunderstorms caused flooding
OL,7,Facross the Midlands last month. It's
OL,8,Fbelieved the flooding is a result of
OL,9,Fheavy rain pushing open the drains.
OL,11,FSharon's daughter Kirsty believes the
OL,12,Frain has pushed the drains open,
OL,13,Fincluding one right in the middle of
OL,14,Fthe estate.
OL,16,FShe said: "There's sanitary products,
OL,17,Fyou can just imagine everything that
OL,18,Fyou put down the toilet is in our
OL,19,Fhomes.
