OL,6,F"Sheer panic, panic, distraught. They
OL,7,Fdon't know which way to turn."
OL,9,FIn a statement, Severn Trent Water
OL,10,Ftold us:
OL,12,FJamie, his wife and 12-week-old baby
OL,13,Fhave been forced to move into a hotel
OL,14,Fwhile asbestos is checked in the house
OL,15,Fthey had only just bought a year ago.
OL,16,FThe bottom floor is now completely
OL,17,Fdestroyed.
OL,19,FResidents say they've been in constant
OL,20,Fcontact with Severn Trent, with no
OL,21,Fluck.
